quran[7{c,v,t}:
17,1,"pak hai woh jo le gaya aik raat apne bande ko masjid haraam se daur ki uss masjid taq jis ke mahol ko is ne barket di hai, taakay usay apni kuch nshanyon ka mushahida karaye haqeeqat mein wohi hai sab kuch suneney aur dekhnay wala"
17,2,"hum ne iss se pehlay moose ko kitaab di thi aur ussay bani Israel ke liye zareya hadaayat banaya tha, iss takeed ke sath ke mere siwa kisi ko apna wakeel nah banana"
17,3,"tum unn logon ki aulaad ho jinhein hum ne Nooh ke sath kashti par sawaar kya tha, aur Nooh aik shukar guzaar bandah tha"
17,4,phir hum ne apni kitaab mein bani Israel ko iss baat par bhi mutnabba kar diya tha ke tum do martaba zameen mein fasaad azeem barpaa karo ge aur barri sar kashi dikhao ge
17,5,"aakhir kaar jab unn mein se pehli sar kashi ka mauqa paish aaya, to ae bani Israel , hum ne tumahray muqablay par apne aisay bande uthaye jo nihayat zor aawar thay aur woh tumahray malik mein ghis kar har taraf phail gay yeh aik wada tha jisay poora ho kar hi rehna tha"
17,6,iss ke baad hum ne tumhe unn par ghlbe ka mauqa day diya aur tumhe maal aur aulaad se madad di aur tumhari tadaad pehlay se barha di
17,7,"dekho! tum ne bhalai ki to woh tumahray apne hi liye bhalai thi, aur buraiee ki to woh tumhari apni zaat ke liye buraiee saabit hui phir jab dosray waday ka waqt aaya to hum ne dosray dushmanon ko tum par musallat kya taakay woh tumahray chehray bigaar den aur masjid ( beeet almuqaddas ) mein usi terhan ghis jayen jis terhan pehlay dushman ghse thay aur jis cheez par un ka haath parre ussay tabah kar ke rakh den"
